            "title": "IShowspeed︱大叔死跟甲亢哥訪華5城博流量  榮昌滷鵝網銷增105%",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"林江全程跟著Speed請食滷鵝，成功將榮昌滷鵝變為網上人氣美食。Youtube@IShowspeed\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/950bfb14cfa9523e9b60d335b28afe09/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250410/_2025041010573546535.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">林江全程跟著Speed請食滷鵝，成功將榮昌滷鵝變為網上人氣美食。Youtube@IShowspeed</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>IShowspeed（甲亢哥）成為網絡流量保證。他在訪華期間，有一名穿著東北大棉襖的大叔「榮昌滷鵝哥」全程做「攝石人」，成都、重慶、深圳、香港、長沙追餵Speed食滷鵝，成為網上紅人，僅網上銷售便暴增105%。\n\n</p><h2>請Speed食滷鵝成功出位</h2>\n<p>「榮昌滷鵝哥」林江，是榮昌文旅委以及部分榮昌滷鵝店主。他在Speed訪問中國期間，瞓身追踪，Speed去到哪便追到哪，成都、重慶、深圳、香港、長沙5城無一缺席。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"林江成功借Speed的流量推銷榮昌滷鵝。抖音＠榮昌滷鵝哥    \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6f27fe1a68bc5a618a86b645a235c143/2025-04/001y6PXDly4i0at51hsrmj60ku0tmnnj02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林江成功借Speed的流量推銷榮昌滷鵝。抖音＠榮昌滷鵝哥    \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"林江成功與Speed建立交情，一同拍片。Youtube@IShowspeed\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/801efe31d995d32682be648e96c66669/2025-04/4516564.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林江成功與Speed建立交情，一同拍片。Youtube@IShowspeed\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"林江成功與Speed建立交情，一同拍片。Youtube@IShowspeed\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2d392ad351e29a4b0d8acd4fd84c0cf6/2025-04/4859859__0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林江成功與Speed建立交情，一同拍片。Youtube@IShowspeed\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"林江成功緊貼Speed出訪中國5城市，讓榮昌滷鵝不斷曝光。Youtube@IShowspeed\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4818e5bcfadf255ca280456c49d140d5/2025-04/14545564.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林江成功緊貼Speed出訪中國5城市，讓榮昌滷鵝不斷曝光。Youtube@IShowspeed\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"林江成功緊貼Speed出訪中國5城市，讓榮昌滷鵝不斷曝光。Youtube@IShowspeed\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8225793c8fe7828a4e94c20f6a116333/2025-04/IShowspeed_4556_.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林江成功緊貼Speed出訪中國5城市，讓榮昌滷鵝不斷曝光。Youtube@IShowspeed\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"林江成功緊貼Speed出訪中國5城市，讓榮昌滷鵝不斷曝光。Youtube@IShowspeed\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3e49e9c8be044848b12358127ef1bb9d/2025-04/IShowspeed_45845.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林江成功緊貼Speed出訪中國5城市，讓榮昌滷鵝不斷曝光。Youtube@IShowspeed\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"林江成功緊貼Speed出訪中國5城市，讓榮昌滷鵝不斷曝光。Youtube@IShowspeed\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e29115f83201637cb644386176c7229e/2025-04/IShowspeed_455665.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林江成功緊貼Speed出訪中國5城市，讓榮昌滷鵝不斷曝光。Youtube@IShowspeed\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"林江成功借Speed的流量成為網絡紅人。抖音＠榮昌滷鵝哥    \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1ef690db66123f99acf873e0d3a4bf43/2025-04/qyj.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林江成功借Speed的流量成為網絡紅人。抖音＠榮昌滷鵝哥    \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3445050/IShowspeed%E9%87%8D%E6%85%B6%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E8%81%AF%E6%89%8B%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD-%E7%B6%AD%E8%82%96%E7%B6%AD%E5%A6%99%E7%94%B2%E4%BA%A2%E5%93%A5%E9%A9%9A%E5%98%86\">IShowspeed︱重慶特朗普聯手直播 維肖維妙「甲亢哥」驚嘆</a>\n</p>\n<p>林江每次也帶著一大隻榮昌滷鵝，突破重重的粉絲與保鏢，請Speed食滷鵝，擺明博流量。而無厘頭見稱的Speed，也來者不拒，當場試食，至後期，二人更成為朋友，可以貼身跟著Speed出訪，甚至獲邀上Speed的座駕一起出行。\n\n</p>\n<p>Speed旋風幫助下，林江在網上的人氣也急升，他在追拍Speed時，以不流利英語介紹「Rongchang braised goose（榮昌滷鵝）」，成功讓這款食品廣為網民認識，成為爆款美食。<br/>\n<br/>\n相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3444996/IShowSpeed%E7%94%B2%E4%BA%A2%E5%93%A5%E5%85%A5%E9%A7%90%E5%B0%8F%E7%B4%85%E6%9B%B8-%E5%96%8A%E8%A9%B1%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E4%B8%80%E8%B5%B7%E8%A1%9D\">IShowSpeed｜「甲亢哥」入駐小紅書 喊話網友：一起衝！</a>\n</p>\n<p>據上觀新聞報道，據榮昌商務委相關負責人介紹，原產榮昌的滷鵝，每年銷售大概在500萬隻左右，店家有300餘家（上規模有10餘家）。這次滷鵝全網爆火之後，再次進行了調查，發現滷鵝線上訂單平均增長了105%左右，個別企業訂單成倍增長。\n\n</p>\n<p>他解釋，因為滷鵝是現制產品，必須每天現制當天發貨，保質期只有7天，這也導致個別企業直接賣斷貨，不得不暫停了網上連結。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2063138/即時-中國-IShowspeed︱大叔死跟甲亢哥訪華5城博流量-榮昌滷鵝網銷增105",
